text: Homonoea uniformis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Karl Jordan in 1894. It is known from Sanghir, Indonesia and Borneo.BioLib.cz - Homonoea uniformis. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1894
title: Homonoea uniformis
